attributes.review: So I downloaded this app to see why it was getting so much hype. But right when I opened the app trump asked for my number. I closed it right away because I got scared. The app then kept sending me notifications saying how trump wanted to be my sugar daddy. I was obviously flattered with this offer but I obviously declined. Trying to forget about this whole thing, I turned on the tv and there was a trump commercial on and trump came out the tv and he was completely naked. I screamed and ran to my room, locking the door behind me. I was in my room for a minute until I starting smelling a putrid stench. I opened the door and he was POOPING on my carpet when there’s a bathroom right beside my room. After about 10 minutes I opened the door to poop smeared in the carpet saying that he would buy me anything I wanted if I didn’t tell anyone about this. I went out in my living room after that to see both of my dogs and my bird laying on the floor skinned. I broke down and started crying. I immediately deleted the app hoping that everything would stop but it hasn’t. Whatever you do, if you don’t want to be cursed, DO NOT DOWNLOAD.
